            </tgroup>
          </informaltable></para>

        <para>Publishes an ESDL service definition to the system
        datastore.</para>

        <para>Examples:</para>

        <programlisting>esdl publish mathservice mathservice.ecm -s nnn.nnn.nnn.nnn --port 8010
</programlisting>
      </sect2>

